  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">DFID&#x2019;s Better Delivery Department (BDD) is leading on the development of a new central service for Due Diligence within DFID. The aim of the Hub is to improve the efficiency and effectiveness of the Due Diligence Assessment process by conducting more central reviews, pooling technical skills and managing contracting-out for specialist services for (finance, auditing, safeguarding and procurement skills).</narrative>
